HEADWORD: Marsupial
<hw>Mar*su"pi*al</hw> <pr>(m⟦aum⟧r*s⟦umac⟧"p⟦icr⟧*⟦ait⟧l)</pr>,
<pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F. <ets>marsupial</ets>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
